                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Mediocre, irregular.</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, vivid red.</seg>
                        Scribe: Walda Śǝllāse. Walda Śǝllāse
                        is mentioned as the scribe in the supplication on <locus target="#40va">40va</locus>.<date>Second half of 20th century</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>ይካ፡ for ይበል፡ ካህን፡</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the scribe; some letters in
                           nomina sacra alternating with black letter (fols. 23rb, 24rb); incipit of
                           Text I and its subsections; titles of the books to be read; one or two
                           initial lines of prayers to be read; numbers of the prayers; directives
                           to the ministers and their abbreviation (fol. 39vb); the word “amen” in
                           fol. 24va; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic
                           numerals. 
 On the incipit page of Text I (fol.3r), a few lines are
                           rubricated (alternating with black lines).</seg>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h2" script="Ethiopic">The quality of the handwriting declines
                        towards the end of the
                        text.</handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>

                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d1">
                        <locus target="#2r">2r</locus> (incipit of Text I): elaborate, coloured
                        (red, black, green) ornamental band, with three lateral extensions;
                        interlaces, floral motifs.</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Doodles and pen trials in fols: 1r, 1v, 2r, 2v, 14v, 23v, 40v, 41r, 41v.</item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
